text: Piedras Gordas is a corregimiento in La Pintada District, Coclé Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 4,164 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 3,648; its population as of 2000 was 3,638. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Coclé Province
